Description: Agent Key Proxy — credential broker daemon for AI agents on Linux
 akprx sits between your AI agent and external APIs.
 The agent sends requests through akprx, which injects the real
 API credentials internally and returns only the response.
 The agent never sees a token, key, or password.
 .
 Runs as a locked system user on localhost only.
 Managed via the akprx CLI.

